sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant WebSocket/SSE
    participant AllClients

    User->>Client: Completes Action (e.g., task, achievement)
    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/scores/increment (JWT, actionId, actionType, metadata)
    API->>API: Authenticate & Validate Request
    API->>API: Update Score, Recalculate Rank
    API->>WebSocket/SSE: Broadcast SCOREUPDATE
    WebSocket/SSE->>AllClients: Update UI in Real Time
